sequenceDiagram
    participant Mobile
    participant Backend
    participant DesktopApp

    DesktopApp->>Backend: Connect (WebSocket)
    Backend-->>DesktopApp: Welcome (incl. IP)
    
    DesktopApp->>DesktopApp: Render QR Code (ws://IP:3001)
    
    Mobile->>Backend: Connect (WebSocket)
    Backend-->>Mobile: Welcome
    
    Mobile->>Backend: Send Command {type: "PLAY"}
    Backend->>DesktopApp: Broadcast {type: "PLAY"}
    DesktopApp->>DesktopApp: Execute Play Action
